    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="publish-30-seo-articles-per-month-for-99-stacc-han"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Health, finance, and legal content requires verified expertise. Google holds this content to higher standards. An article about tax strategies written by a CPA outranks AI content on the same topic. The credentials matter as much as the words.</p></div></div>
